'''[[Mexico]]''' competed at the '''[[1932 Summer Olympics]]''' in [[Los Angeles, California|Los Angeles]], [[United States]]. 73 competitors, 71 men and 2 women, took part in 52 events in 12 sports.<ref name="sports-reference">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/MEX/summer/1932/ |title=Mexico at the 1932 Los Angeles Summer Games |accessdate=2010-05-03 |work=sports-reference.com}}</ref>
