==Inconsistency==

The article's history is not entirely clear; mention is made of a prior structure on the same site (by the same name?) but only the current building's history is outlined. However, despite the current building being opened in 1950, this site is noted as the home of the Quebec Bulldogs from 1910-1920. If anyone can expand on this, please feel free. [[User:Duncan1800|Duncan1800]] ([[User talk:Duncan1800|talk]]) 04:38, 21 July 2008 (UTC)

==Title / Language==

There seems to be some inconsistency in the first sentence of the article.  It says "Colisée Pepsi (English: Pepsi Coliseum), formerly the Colisée de Québec (English: The Quebec Coliseum)...".  However, this is the English Wikipedia.  Thus, if the names, in English, really are/were "X Coliseum", then the name of this article should be "Pepsi Coliseum".  Alternately, if it's called "Colisée Pepsi" in English (we use all sorts of foreign-origin names in English - we don't call the Autobahn "the Car Road"), then the first sentence should not say (English: ) - because its name, in English, should be the title of the article already! Looking at the English version of their own website (http://www.expocite.com/www/colisee-pepsi.php), it appears that they call it the "Pepsi Coliseum" when they're speaking English.  That's a strong argument, but there may be other, more important sources.  If it turns out that "Pepsi Coliseum" is far more prevalent in English, then we should change the title of the article.  I'll do that in a few days if no one replies to this, or if there are only messages of support.  Otherwise, let's talk about it.  Cheers, [[User:AshleyMorton|AshleyMorton]] ([[User talk:AshleyMorton|talk]]) 02:29, 25 October 2011 (UTC)
* Huh - well, I placed this note here a year and a half ago, and got no response. I've done some digging, and can only come up with sources that call it the "Coliseum" or the "Pepsi Coliseum". Lacking contradictions, let's move this to "Pepsi Coliseum". [[User:AshleyMorton|AshleyMorton]] ([[User talk:AshleyMorton|talk]]) 22:31, 8 July 2013 (UTC)

